戏的更多信息。</p><p>与此同时，在游戏最新预告片发布后，粉丝们<a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/call-of-duty-modern-warfare-3-trailer-teases-return-of-controversial-no-russian-mission-3480538"><ins>猜测</ins></a><em>《现代战争 3》</em>将包含对 2009 年推出的<em>《现代战争 II》</em>原版<a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/mwii-modern-warfare-ii-warzone-2-no-russian-170044023.html"><em><ins>《现代</ins></em>战争 II》中备受争议的“禁止俄罗斯”任务的更新<ins>。去年的《现代战争 2》重启版中并没有</ins></a>这个关卡。 。 </p><div id="d840765049304445856bc0d478c44643"><div style="left:0;width:100%;height:0;position:relative;padding-bottom:56.25%;"><iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/C_6J06wdgXY?rel=0" style="top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;position:absolute;border:0;" allowfullscreen="" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></div><p></p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上，网址为 https://www.engadget.com/call-of-duty-players-can-bring-most-of-their-modern-warfare-ii-gear-over-to-modern-warfare -iii-170024613.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/call-of-duty-players-can-bring-most-of-their-modern-warfare-ii-gear-over-to-modern-warfare-iii-170024613.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> f1e49b99-227e-4ef8-ae5d-dd7aa5d4f2d3</guid><dc:creator>克里斯·霍尔特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Thu, 10 Aug 2023 17:00:24 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1691685995</ingested><modified> 2023-08-10T16:47:04+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Finance Trading]]></category><category><![CDATA[Consumer Discretionary]]></category><category><![CDATA[Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[Video Games]]></category><category><![CDATA[Sports & Recreation]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Kris Holt]]></category><media:content height="1080" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/0f43a740-3799-11ee-bf77-414503a8b046" width="1920"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1080" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/0f43a740-3799-11ee-bf77-414503a8b046" width="1920"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Activision]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[A collection of Call of Duty badges, weapons and characters.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Call of Duty badges, weapons and operators]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[The best smart speakers for 2023]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>语音助手现在无处不在——在你的手机上、你的电视上，甚至可能在你的厨房用具上。但人们与 Siri、Alexa 和 Google Assistant 互动的最常见方式之一是通过智能扬声器，而且现在有各种不同价位的此类设备。拥有始终监听唤醒词的智能家居设备也有缺点，因为向亚马逊、苹果和谷歌提供更多个人信息可能是一个值得怀疑的决定。也就是说，所有这些公司都让管理数据的使用方式变得更加容易——你可以选择不让人工审查你的一些语音查询，而且使用各种数字助理管理和删除你的历史记录也更简单。</p><p>好消息是，现在是购买智能扬声器的最佳时机，特别是如果您是音乐迷。尽管有很多好处，最初的 Amazon Echo 和 Google Home 设备听起来并不好。另一方面，Sonos 制造了音质出色的 WiFi 连接扬声器，但缺乏任何语音控制智能功能。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>现在一切都变了。 Sonos 于 2022 年发布了自己的语音助手，并在其最新的扬声器上支持 Alexa。与此同时，谷歌和亚马逊通过最新的扬声器在音质方面取得了巨大的进步。即使是像 Echo Dot 和 Nest Mini 这样的低端型号听起来也比早期版本要好得多。随着这些扬声器的日益普及，现在有比以往更多的选择。让我们来看看我们精选的不同价位和不同用途的最佳智能扬声器。</p><h2>挑选助理</h2><p>大多数人应该做的第一件事是决定他们想要使用什么语音助手。 Google Assistant 和亚马逊的 Alexa 都是得到良好支持的选项，并且不断发展，新功能不断添加。几年前，Alexa 与更多的智能家居设备配合使用，但目前，基本上任何值得购买的智能设备都可以同时使用这两种设备。</p><p>这主要是个人喜好的问题。如果您已经在 Android 手机上使用 Google Assistant，那么坚持使用 Google Assistant 是有意义的。不过，虽然 Alexa 不太擅长回答常识性问题，但它可以很好地与 Google 帐户中的日历等内容同步。它也可以与最广泛的智能家居设备配合使用。如果您从未使用过<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL2FwcHMuYXBwbGUuY29tL3VzL2FwcC9hbWF6b24tYWxleGEvaWQ5NDQwMTE2MjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6IjIyZTNmMGI3LWMxNzktMzkyYS04MjFjLWU2ZGY1M2MyODBhNiJ9&amp;signature=AQAAARYWVaYBWoXE3saOh9reSP5jBvl5JqgaMir5u_WYF0GM&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.apple.com%2Fus%2Fapp%2Famazon-alexa%2Fid944011620">Alexa</a>或<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3BsYXkuZ29vZ2xlLmNvbS9zdG9yZS9hcHBzL2RldGFpbHM_aWQ9Y29tLmdvb2dsZS5hbmRyb2lkLmFwcHMuZ29vZ2xlYXNzaXN0YW50JmhsPWVuX1VTJmdsPVVTIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiIyMmUzZjBiNy1jMTc5LTM5MmEtODIxYy1lNmRmNTNjMjgwYTYifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAdocdFrFh3jxXbyI2jt8pzj7IYj1eQKc51OO9U0yOHE0&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.google.android.apps.googleassistant%26hl%3Den_US%26gl%3DUS">Google Assistant</a> ，您可以将它们的应用程序下载到您的智能手机上，并在购买扬声器之前花一些时间进行测试。</p><p>如果您购买带有麦克风的 Sonos 设备，您还可以使用<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/sonos-voice-control-assistant-for-music-200538441.html">该公司自己的语音助手</a>，由 Giancarlo Esposito 配音。它纯粹专注于音乐控制，因此您不会用它来执行发送消息或询问天气预报等操作。但作为音乐助手，Sonos 语音控制通常相当快速且可靠。</p><p>至于 Apple，您不会惊讶地发现 HomePod 和 HomePod mini 是市场上唯一兼容 Siri 的扬声器。苹果的 Siri 因不如 Alexa 或 Google Assistant 智能而闻名，但它完全能够处理常见的语音查询，例如回答问题、控制智能家居设备、发送消息、拨打电话和流媒体音乐。从技术上讲，Siri 和苹果的 HomeKit 技术并不像竞争对手那样适用于那么多智能家居设备，但找到兼容的设备并不难。在过去的几年里，苹果无疑改进了 Siri 的功能，提供了方便的功能，例如利用 HomePod 和 HomePod Mini 中内置温度传感器的对讲工具和例程。</p><h2> 50 美元以下最佳智能音箱：Amazon Echo Dot</h2><p><core-commerce id="d9b8d32fabd14ba39688ca99f80af4ce" data-type="product-list"></p><p>大多数人进入智能音箱世界的切入点都不会是昂贵的设备。亚马逊的第四代<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMDlCOFYxTFozP3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLWQ2LTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiIyMmUzZjBiNy1jMTc5LTM5MmEtODIxYy1lNmRmNTNjMjgwYTYifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAZXNEHk7FsGNE_XvtNGqcNRKg4X5smBOvwFOgWVpzaOU&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB09B8V1LZ3%3F">Echo Dot</a>和谷歌的<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Walmart;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=3719d8d4-5edd-4817-998a-91f3229e7323&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Walmart&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAWI09cTB1paP_8rNk0Y7QX-pWjYPXnnM13p5n65pcwPv&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.walmart.com%2Fip%2FGoogle-Nest-Mini-2nd-Generation-Chalk%2F751612012">Nest Mini</a>是最明显的起点，有两个重要原因。第一，它们很便宜：Nest Mini 和 Echo Dost 的售价都是 50 美元。二是他们有能力。尽管价格低廉，这些扬声器实际上可以完成与更大、更昂贵的设备相同的功能。</p><p> Google Nest Mini 于 2019 年底发布，但亚马逊去年刚刚更新了 Echo Dot。对于大多数人来说，Echo Dot 是最好的小型智能扬声器。亚马逊不断改进其 Echo 设备系列的音频性能，Echo Dot 也不例外。它产生的声音比我对 50 美元扬声器的预期要响亮、清晰得多。 Nest Mini 听起来不错，非常适合在卧室里聆听，同时为新的一天做好准备，但 Echo Dot 是一款更好的通用音乐聆听设备。</p><p>从设计角度来看，亚马逊推出了最新的 Echo Dot，打破了常规。新款 Dot 的形状像一个小地球仪，而不是像 Nest Mini 那样的小冰球。它比 Nest Mini 大得多，但这样的尺寸为它提供了容纳高端音频组件的空间。虽然大部分情况下是免提的，但 Dot 将物理音量按钮和静音开关保留在顶部，以及一个用于激活 Alexa 语音控制的按钮。虽然 Dot 看起来不像 Nest Mini 那样时尚，但拥有物理按钮可以更轻松地调节音量和使麦克风静音。我确实希望 Dot 有一种方法可以物理暂停音乐；在 Nest Mini 上，如果您点击设备的中间，音乐就会停止。</p><p>总的来说，Dot 对于大多数人来说是最好的预算选择，但我会毫不犹豫地推荐 Nest Mini 作为另一个经济实惠的智能扬声器选择。与 Alexa 相比，我通常更喜欢使用 Google Assistant，任​​何有同感的人都应该购买 Nest Mini。 Dot 的听起来确实明显更好，所以如果您打算定期听音频，那么这可能是正确的选择。但是，如果您只打算在早上准备时使用它来播放一首快歌或播客，只需选择您最喜欢的助手并从那里开始即可。</p><h2> 100 美元以下最佳智能音箱：Amazon Echo</h2><p><core-commerce id="4071c4bc3ab14a62b2e309bc135efb14" data-type="product-list"></p><p>亚马逊、苹果和谷歌都有 100 美元的智能音箱：分别是第四代<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMDg1SEs0S0w2P3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLWQ2LTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiIyMmUzZjBiNy1jMTc5LTM5MmEtODIxYy1lNmRmNTNjMjgwYTYifQ&amp;signature=AQAAATdcQZxdYwTZKlKR3f8wqWL47-eHL5SKRgMmwrEYltFC&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB085HK4KL6%3F">Echo</a> 、 <a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Walmart;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=3719d8d4-5edd-4817-998a-91f3229e7323&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Walmart&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiIzNzE5ZDhkNC01ZWRkLTQ4MTctOTk4YS05MWYzMjI5ZTczMjMiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cud2FsbWFydC5jb20vaXAvSG9tZVBvZC1taW5pLVNwYWNlLUdyYXkvODEwNzQ2OTYxIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiIyMmUzZjBiNy1jMTc5LTM5MmEtODIxYy1lNmRmNTNjMjgwYTYifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAXA5tlqyG6X6C9ACOSTnyb27FaC-pkRyIPk1k08C52Vf&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.walmart.com%2Fip%2FHomePod-mini-Space-Gray%2F810746961">HomePod mini</a>和<a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Walmart;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=3719d8d4-5edd-4817-998a-91f3229e7323&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Walmart&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAfTf66g1NcLyueHahQ7Wo_B-ftmspS_GfKNyJWMUNylN&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.walmart.com%2Fip%2FGoogle-Nest-Audio-Smart-Speaker-with-Google-Assistant-Chalk%2F778990339">Nest Audio</a> 。这三个公司都声称具有卓越的音频质量，因此对于很多人来说，这些扬声器将是 Echo Dot 和 Nest Mini 等小型扬声器与 Sonos Era 100 等更大、更昂贵的型号之间的最佳选择。</p><p>亚马逊再次超越了自己的实力。与 Dot 一样，最新的 Echo 也经过了彻底重新设计，新的内部结构也是以音乐为中心而设计的。它结合了一个 3 英寸低音扬声器和两个 0.8 英寸高音扬声器——比 Nest Audio 或 HomePod mini 更先进的设置。 （Google Nest Audio 使用一个 3 英寸低音扬声器，但只有一个 0.75 英寸高音扬声器，而 Apple HomePod mini 则使用一个“全频”驱动器和两个无源散热器。）</p><p>实际上，这意味着 Echo 明显比 Nest Audio 或 HomePod mini 响亮，并且比竞争对手更适合播放充满房间的声音。它还提供令人印象深刻的低音重击和强大的中频。事实上，我对扬声器的主要抱怨是高音不够清脆。将 Echo 与 Era 100 进行比较，100 听起来更加活泼，而 Echo 则显得有点浑浊。不过，100 的价格是 Echo 的两倍多。</p><p>虽然 Echo 扬声器可能在音量和低音方面击败 Nest Audio 和 HomePod mini，但谷歌和苹果的扬声器也是不错的选择。 HomePod mini 是三款扬声器中最安静的，但它在整个音频频谱中听起来仍然很平衡。低音不是太自信，但鉴于其微小的尺寸（它是迄今为止这三个扬声器中最小的），其存在感比我预期的要强。</p><p>如果您使用的是 iPhone 11 或更新机型，它还有一些不错的好处。得益于最近 iPhone 中的 U1“超宽带”芯片，HomePod mini 可以判断附近是否有手机，这使得将音乐从手机传递到扬声器（反之亦然）变得非常简单。 HomePod mini 的播放控件也会自动弹出，如果扬声器当前未播放，手机的锁定屏幕将显示音乐建议。设置也非常简单——只需将 iPhone 或 iPad 靠近扬声器，它就会自动启动该过程。</p><p>谷歌的 Nest Audio 听起来也相当好听。它的声音比 HomePod mini 稍大一些，并且低音更强。它的整体功率和表现力不如 Echo，但 100 美元的价格，它是一款平衡性良好的扬声器，应该可以满足大多数人的需求。</p><p>如果您想要更大的音量或渴望更身临其境的体验，所有这三个扬声器都支持立体声配对。只需 200 美元，两台 Echo 就能让整个大房间充满高品质的声音和足够的低音，足以为派对提供动力。一对 HomePod mini 或 Nest Audio 扬声器的功能不是那么强大，但如果您是一个更热心的听众，那么它可以带来很大的升级。工作日期间，一对 Nest Audio 或 HomePod 迷你扬声器放在我的办公桌上听起来很棒。我不需要压倒性的音量，但可以欣赏立体声分离度。其中两个扬声器一起可以轻松为更大的生活空间提供动力，尽管如果优先考虑音量，Echo 是更好的选择。</p><p>在这里，我也认为选择最适合您家中以及与其他小工具配合使用的智能助手可能是最重要的因素 - 但考虑到 Alexa 的无处不在和新 Echo 的卓越音质，它是这个价位上最好的智能扬声器。</p><h2>最佳中端智能音箱：Sonos Era 100</h2><p><core-commerce id="25a95ee9632047bdbbbbb900dbf8b94a" data-type="product-list"></p><p>如果你对音乐只是一时的兴趣，那么 Echo Dot 和 Nest Mini 并不能真正满足你的需求。花更多的钱升级到在设计时考虑到音频质量的扬声器是我做出的最佳决定之一。多年来，我一直没有合适的家庭音乐解决方案，但最终，适度的投资让我的生活变得更加愉快。</p><p>多年来，Sonos One 一直是我的最爱，它结合了合理的价格、良好的音质和大量有用的功能，如简单的多房间音频、立体声配对以及与大量服务的兼容性。今年，Sonos 用<a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Sonos;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=1e71dc69-0ad7-47e7-abf5-dc3926557fa3&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Sonos&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiIxZTcxZGM2OS0wYWQ3LTQ3ZTctYWJmNS1kYzM5MjY1NTdmYTMiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc29ub3MuY29tL2VuLXVzL3Nob3AvZXJhLTEwMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiMjJlM2YwYjctYzE3OS0zOTJhLTgyMWMtZTZkZjUzYzI4MGE2In0&amp;signature=AQAAAZ2QTRvlnA5n8O6YgARV32cka-FgDMGabeYoGRrBpYQW&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sonos.com%2Fen-us%2Fshop%2Fera-100">Era 100</a>取代了 One，这是一款售价 250 美元的扬声器，几乎在您能想到的所有方面都有所改进。最重要的是，它使用了一种新的扬声器阵列，其中包括两个高音扬声器（而不是只有一个）以及一个大 25% 的低音扬声器。最终的结果是，Era 100 在音质方面轻而易举地超越了 One，具有令人印象深刻的低音、令人惊讶的巨大音量以及由于额外的高音扬声器而提高的高端清晰度。</p><p>除了音质之外，还有很多其他改进。 Era 100 使用内置麦克风更轻松地进行 Trueplay 调音，从而根据您放置的位置优化扬声器的输出。以前，您必须使用 iPhone 在房间里走动并挥舞手机才能优化您的 Sonos 扬声器，但现在这个过程要简单得多。 Era 100 还包括通过 USB-C 端口的线路输入，并且当您只想快速将设备连接到扬声器时还具有蓝牙功能。令人遗憾的是，您需要购买适配器才能将转盘或其他音频设备连接到 Era 100，但由于 One 根本不支持线路输入，我仍然很高兴它是一种选择。</p><p>还有一些其他小而扎实的改进，例如重新设计的顶部控件，可以更轻松地跳过曲目，以及麦克风静音开关，可以切断麦克风的电源以提供额外的安全性。与 One 一样，在这里设置 Alexa 或 Sonos 语音助手很容易，但 Era 100<em>不</em>支持 Google Assistant - 因此，如果您以前使用 Sonos 扬声器并依赖 Google，那么您很不幸地不走运这里。不过，除了这一变化之外，Era 100 是一款出色的全能性能产品。它本身就是一款很棒的扬声器，如果您想构建多房间音频设置，它也是一个很好的起点。</p><p> Amazon Echo Studio 仍然是一款音质出色的扬声器，价格为 199 美元，也比 Era 100 便宜很多。如果您想节省一些现金，或者您的智能家居生态系统中已经拥有一堆其他 Echo 设备，那么将其作为更高质量音乐播放的扬声器是有意义的。但考虑到今年秋天它就已经上市四年了，我认为选择一款能够获得更长时间支持和更新的新设备是有意义的。</p><h2>最适合音乐爱好者的智能音箱：Sonos Five</h2><p><core-commerce id="a60083cdb64d44758943efa1a26eb1e4" data-type="product-list"></p><p>尽管 Era 100 和 Echo Studio 非常出色，但您能从它们中获得的功能也有限。如果您渴望更多的低音、清晰度和立体声分离度，550 美元的<a data-i13n="cpos:10;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Sonos;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=1e71dc69-0ad7-47e7-abf5-dc3926557fa3&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Sonos&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiIxZTcxZGM2OS0wYWQ3LTQ3ZTctYWJmNS1kYzM5MjY1NTdmYTMiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc29ub3MuY29tL2VuLXVzL3Nob3AvZml2ZSIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiMjJlM2YwYjctYzE3OS0zOTJhLTgyMWMtZTZkZjUzYzI4MGE2In0&amp;signature=AQAAAR25cLMb2vxNkMKEVe6NeoOcX395yZzkj30eSdpml_uG&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sonos.com%2Fen-us%2Fshop%2Ffive">Sonos Five</a>是此列表中音质最好的智能扬声器。它具有 Era 100 的许多便利性，并且听起来比任何其他 Sonos 扬声器都要好。它听起来也比 Echo Studio 和谷歌目前销售的任何产品都要好得多。</p><p>也就是说，五号扩展了我们对智能扬声器的定义，因为它没有内置语音助手。但它在音乐播放方面非常出色，值得推荐您与 Echo Dot 或 Nest Mini 一起使用。 Both of those speakers work with Sonos, so you can use voice commands to control the Five just as you would a dedicated Alexa or Google Assistant device. Sonos also refreshed the speaker two years ago with a new wireless radio as well as more memory and a faster processor. This means it should stay current and work with future Sonos software updates for years to come.</p><p> Since we&#39;re talking &quot;best&quot; here, I&#39;m going to go ahead and recommend that true music junkies splash out on two Five speakers and pair them in stereo. Put simply, it&#39;s the most enjoyable experience I&#39;ve had listening to music in years; I found myself picking up new details while listening to albums I&#39;ve heard over and over again. It&#39;s a wonderful experience and worth saving for if you&#39;re a music lover. I didn&#39;t know what I was missing until I tried the Five.</p><p> The Sonos <a data-i13n="cpos:11;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Sonos;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=1e71dc69-0ad7-47e7-abf5-dc3926557fa3&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Sonos&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiIxZTcxZGM2OS0wYWQ3LTQ3ZTctYWJmNS1kYzM5MjY1NTdmYTMiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc29ub3MuY29tL2VuLXVzL3Nob3AvZXJhLTMwMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiMjJlM2YwYjctYzE3OS0zOTJhLTgyMWMtZTZkZjUzYzI4MGE2In0&amp;signature=AQAAAVjDDSsafMZzXOPRzL6yDO_3xbdyYsxSHlScfT0ot5w0&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sonos.com%2Fen-us%2Fshop%2Fera-300">Era 300</a> , also recently released, is a $450 speaker that supports Dolby Atmos spatial audio from Apple Music and Amazon Music Unlimited. I&#39;ve found that the quality of spatial audio mixes can be very hit or miss, but the good news is that the Era 300 sounds outstanding whether it&#39;s playing back Atmos content or just standard tracks. It&#39;s not quite as good as the Sonos Five, but it does have built-in microphones for voice assistants and easy Trueplay tuning as well as Bluetooth and the redesigned controls on the Era 100. Again, the main downside is that Google Assistant isn&#39;t supported here.</p><p> Finally, if you&#39;re an Apple Music user or have a lot of Apple hardware in your home, the second-generation <a data-i13n="cpos:12;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Apple;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=4130e2f0-a14f-4c5e-bdab-cd52ac7d8e79&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Apple&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI0MTMwZTJmMC1hMTRmLTRjNWUtYmRhYi1jZDUyYWM3ZDhlNzkiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYXBwbGUuY29tL2hvbWVwb2QvIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiIyMmUzZjBiNy1jMTc5LTM5MmEtODIxYy1lNmRmNTNjMjgwYTYifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAZLnR3S2KbD5Q6PLJUnEcdOnwGDQLbiRbs0LzN41wTFq&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.apple.com%2Fhomepod%2F">HomePod</a> is definitely worth considering. At $300, it&#39;s a lot cheaper than these Sonos speakers but supports spatial audio like the Era 300. The Era 300 and Sonos Five are better speakers overall (and certainly much louder), but there&#39;s a lot to like about the HomePod&#39;s audio quality at its price point. It&#39;s a clear, crisp vocal-forward speaker, and its design and software processing does a great job of making music sound like it&#39;s all around you, even if you&#39;re not playing back Dolby Atmos tracks.</p><h2> Best portable smart speaker: Sonos Roam</h2><p><core-commerce id="ad8441cad45a4faabcbc0e9b04740ef1" data-type="product-list"></p><p> While many people will be happy with a few speakers strategically placed throughout their home, you might want something that works outside as well as inside. Fortunately, you can find speakers that pair voice controls and strong music playback performance with portable, weatherproof form factors. For my money, it&#39;s hard to beat the <a data-i13n="cpos:13;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Sonos;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=1e71dc69-0ad7-47e7-abf5-dc3926557fa3&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Sonos&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiIxZTcxZGM2OS0wYWQ3LTQ3ZTctYWJmNS1kYzM5MjY1NTdmYTMiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc29ub3MuY29tL2VuLXVzL3Nob3Avcm9hbSIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiMjJlM2YwYjctYzE3OS0zOTJhLTgyMWMtZTZkZjUzYzI4MGE2In0&amp;signature=AQAAAeq2_H9R60wVGN9EP4TrWro8mlqbdOt9_4uJX6UE_CCp&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sonos.com%2Fen-us%2Fshop%2Froam">Sonos Roam</a> for sheer versatility, not to mention audio quality.</p><p> When used inside the home, the Roam works like any other Sonos speaker. It fits in with an existing multi-room Sonos setup, or you can get a pair for stereo playback. Like most other Sonos speakers, it works with the Sonos Voice Assistant, Google Assistant or Amazon Alexa, and it supports essentially every major music service available. It sounds very good given its tiny size; it&#39;s quieter and not quite as clear as the Sonos One or the Era 100, but it still packs a surprising bass thump and distinct highs.</p><p> Since it was designed with on-the-go usage in mind, the Roam has a battery and Bluetooth so you can take it anywhere and use it far away from your WiFi network. And its diminutive size makes it easy to take it everywhere, both around the house and out and about. It&#39;s also the first Sonos speaker that is fully waterproof, as well as dust- and drop-resistant, so you shouldn&#39;t worry about taking it to the pool or beach.</p><p> The Roam gets about 10 hours of battery life, whether you&#39;re on WiFI or Bluetooth. There are other portable speakers that last longer, so if you&#39;re really going to push the battery you might be better served by another option.</p><p> Another wireless speaker option is the Sonos <a data-i13n="cpos:14;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Sonos;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=1e71dc69-0ad7-47e7-abf5-dc3926557fa3&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Sonos&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiIxZTcxZGM2OS0wYWQ3LTQ3ZTctYWJmNS1kYzM5MjY1NTdmYTMiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc29ub3MuY29tL2VuLXVzL3Nob3AvbW92ZSIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiMjJlM2YwYjctYzE3OS0zOTJhLTgyMWMtZTZkZjUzYzI4MGE2In0&amp;signature=AQAAAf9M3XjMC0rhmFH7biYEPUpkOqa2PQFYcaozlglnQTbi&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sonos.com%2Fen-us%2Fshop%2Fmove">Move</a> . It&#39;s much larger and louder than the Roam and has better sound quality, which it should given that it costs $400. But, rumors indicate Sonos is getting ready to replace it this fall with a new model. With that in mind, I&#39;d recommend most people interested in a speaker like this wait to see what Sonos has coming up – $400 is a lot of money to spend on hardware that&#39;s about to be replaced.</p><p> A better choice than the Move, unless you already have other Sonos products, is the $399 <a data-i13n="cpos:15;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAcJ8lMPA4i0iXXFpC6cy2D1NxIuyoKaZL6BUuU7fBz7v&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FBose-Portable-Home-Speaker-Built%2Fdp%2FB07VFKBQ3K%3Fth%3D1">Bose Portable Smart speaker</a> . It supports Alexa and Google Assistant commands, and since it can connect to WiFi, you can ask your preferred assistant to play music from Spotify, Amazon Music and other services. On top of that, it produces well-rounded sound, sports an IPX4 design with a convenient carry handle and will last up to 12 hours on a single charge.</p><p> Bose also has a good alternative to the Roam. The $149 <a data-i13n="cpos:16;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAWApfm9Tkcg4KZ_ozvq88khu_GJ_3edD8nKreQxBN7lX&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FBose-SoundLink-Bluetooth-Portable-Waterproof%2Fdp%2FB099TJGJ91%3Fth%3D1">SoundLink Flex</a> supports Siri and Google Assistant commands, plus it has an IP67 design that&#39;s roughly the size of a small clutch bag. It pumps out bright, dynamic sound and can pair with other speakers for stereo sound, too – it&#39;s excellent and slightly cheaper than the Roam.</p><p> While this guide is all about smart speakers, we&#39;d be remiss if we didn&#39;t mention all of the solid portable speakers out there that either have limited smart features or none at all. We have <a data-i13n="cpos:17;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-portable-bluetooth-speakers-133004551.html">an entire guide</a> to the best portable Bluetooth speakers, so if you&#39;re purely concerned with portability and less about having an ecosystem of connected speakers, there are lots of options worth investigating.</p> This article originally appeared on Engadget at https://www.engadget.com/best-smart-speakers-151515264.html?src=rss]]>;</description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/best-smart-speakers-151515264.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 22e3f0b7-c179-392a-821c-e6df53c280a6</guid><dc:creator> Nathan Ingraham</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Thu, 10 Aug 2023 16:46:05 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 